{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_14_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央 3話 『愛おしいと思う瞬間』ね",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ゲームが発売される数日前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日の莉央さんの仕事は、もし恋のプロモーション用の\n写真撮影と、雑誌のインタビューか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.5333334208
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様\n着替えてきたけど、この衣装はどうかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.0883221085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.9666667541
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "とても良く似合っています\n仕事の出来る女性って感じで格好いいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう\nこれで貴方も私と結婚したくなったんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.7000000875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですね……\n莉央さんがパートナーなら心強いかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.3333334208
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "それ、恋愛のパートナーじゃなくて\n仕事のパートナーとして頼りになるって意味でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……別にいいわよ\n貴方に気の利いたセリフなんて期待してないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.999999237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.9999993245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……。でも、似合っていると思ったのは\n本当ですよ。これならゲームもきっと評判になります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.8666659911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "当然よ。みんなが私に恋をするように\n気合いを入れて作ったんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "貴方も覚悟してプレイすることね\n私にプロポーズしたくなっても知らないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.8333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.6666661579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、そうですね。恋愛ゲームのヒロインと\n言われても実感がわかなくて、最初は苦労しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4999994913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.2752151488
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "私の恋愛観をここまで深く掘り下げたのは初めてで\n今までにない神崎莉央の新たな一面を出せたと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2000033061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（もうすぐ発売されるもし恋について）\n（莉央さんが雑誌のインタビューに答えているが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5333366394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.6333456279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（スーツ姿が様になり過ぎて、アイドルと言うより）\n（会社の広報担当社員のような雰囲気だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3288681096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.9000122946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームの中で一番好きなシーンですか？\nそうですね、どのシーンも思い入れはあるんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.4513534605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.1666774353
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "あえて一番を選ぶなら、会社で居眠りしている私の頭を\n恋人が優しく撫でてくれるシーンでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5119602941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "好きな人の寝顔を見て、微笑みながら髪を撫でる……\nなんてことのない日常のワンシーンなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "愛してると言葉に出さなくても、好きな人への想いが\n伝わってくる、素敵なシーンだと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "知ってますか？　好きな人の寝顔を見ながら\n頭を撫でていると、愛おしさで心が満たされるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9000132243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "私の胸に愛しい気持ちが溢れて\n心が幸せで満たされるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.0666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、私はそんな経験はないので\n全部想像ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2000071207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.0875732421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "インタビューお疲れ様です。さっきの「好きな人の頭を\n撫でると幸せで満たされる」って回答凄く良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.0333374022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "大切な人を想う心情をとても具体的に語っていましたが\nあれは映画か何かを参考にされたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.4666656493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.8000194152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。参考にしたものはあるけど……\nそれが何かは秘密よ、ヒ・ミ・ツ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.1397604886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ゲームが発売される数ヶ月前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.9333558003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 177.2333521523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "シナリオの参考にしたいから、私が恋人と、してみたい\nシチュエーションを教えてほしいって言われたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.3333681742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "胸がときめく恋愛の場面なんて、私に聞かれても困るわ\nどういうシーンを提案したらいいのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.3403924591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "好きな人を愛おしいと思うのはどんな時か……何気ない\n日常の中で、この人を好きだと実感する瞬間は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.5666984557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　{user}さんが\n机に顔を埋めて……もしかして、居眠りしてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.0333272296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……早くこの作業を終わらせて……\n打ち合わせに行かないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.6333272296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "今のは寝言？\n夢の中でも仕事に追われてるのは彼らしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.200031789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、俺が付いてます……\n一緒に頑張りましょう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.0711848847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "私の夢を見てるのかしら\n眠りながら心配するなんて筋金入りのマネージャーだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.366660563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "よしよし、いつも頑張ってて偉いわよ\n……あら、貴方の髪って意外と触り心地がいいのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.9000239052,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 245.1333496968
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "こうして撫でていると、なんだか気分が落ち着くわ\nドッグセラピーってこんな感じなのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.1999938963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫……莉央さんと恋したい人、沢山いますから……\nみんな、莉央さんのことが……大好きですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.7999938963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "寝言でも私に気を遣ってるの？\nそれとも、それが貴方の本音なのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.9333272296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
